title: Watch Dak Prescott dominate coach Jason Garrett in a throwing contest
text:
Jan 29, 2017 at 1:39p ET 0Shares 
The Dallas Cowboys’ season ended a few weeks ago in the Divisional Round of the playoffs, but for part of the team, it was extended a bit. Jason Garrett and his coaching staff will lead the NFC squad on Sunday night in the Pro Bowl with seven Cowboys representing the team. 
Dak Prescott is among them, and he didn’t waste any time showing up his coach in a friendly competition. He took on Garrett in a throwing competition as they attempted to throw footballs into basketball hoops. 
Advantage: Dak Prescott.
